Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.96,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazen na! Kiken da!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.63,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Yatsura ga aisurya dotanba
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.38,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dontanba ja nai ka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.68,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazeru na! Kiken no nengoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.74,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dotanba tte no sono wake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:54.81,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Sorya maa yatsu ga deatte kara darou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.23,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Tanonja nai shomondai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.28,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Maneku kakeawasette no aru no da
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:02.28,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mou au koto wo tomerya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.49,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Sore de koto wa sumu wake da keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.74,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Iya ni naru you na ki ga tsukya
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.95,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Futari bocchi nan na no karuma kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:16.50,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazeru na! Somosomo deau na!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.78,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Torisetsu ni sa dondake kaitetemo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.51,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Muda saa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.14,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazen na! Kiken da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.89,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Yatsura ga aisurya dotanba
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.52,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dontanba kamau ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.90,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Somosomo hitotsu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.90,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mazen na! Kiken da!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.61,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Yatsura ga aisurya dotanba
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.11,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dontanba kamau ka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:46.11,OP - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Sorosoro ikou ze meifu madou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.96,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.63,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dojde-li ke spojení, zahnán budeš do kouta
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.38,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Jsi už v koutě zahnaný!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.68,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Je to nebezpečné setkání!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.74,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Důvod, proč jsi zahnán do kouta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:54.81,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}S prominutím, příčinou je vaše setkání
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.23,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}To je ta křižovatka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.28,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Co ti způsobuje problémy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:02.28,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Pokud jim zabráníme v setkání
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.49,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Tak bude vše v pořádku
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:08.22,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Špatný pocit z toho mám a když jsem si to uvědomil
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.95,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ti dva byli spolu. Je to karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:16.50,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Nemluv s nimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.78,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Na manuálu tolik nesejde
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:24.51,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Je to zbytečné
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.14,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.89,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dojde-li ke spojení, zahnán budeš do kouta
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.52,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Záleží ti na klidném životě?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.90,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}S tím měl jsi začít
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.90,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nepleť se do toho! Je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.61,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Pokud se spojí, budeš zahnán do kouta
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.11,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Záleží ti na klidném životě?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:46.11,OP - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nastal čas jít do tajemné říše mrtvých
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:25.86,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kyoufu ni obietatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:29.57,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Uchikatsu hodo no taori wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:32.99,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Omottau koto warashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:36.37,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Yami ni hikari uedoshite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:40.04,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Michibikarete sentaku shite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:43.63,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mizu kara eranda michi na noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:47.34,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mayoi doori saa mayottari nayandari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:51.35,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Demo iku shikanai darou tatoe subete kaketemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:55.85,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Zutto kakko mo ima mo mirai mo kanarazu ni motteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:59.60,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Dare ni mo makenai tsuyoi ishi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:03.15,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Owari koto mo naku susumu kimetai ten toppa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:07.78,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Zetsubou wo kibou ni kaete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:11.82,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hero nanpaku tachi agare
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:15.12,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Hero mamorou jishin sa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:19.17,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kitto Rival to tomo ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:23.80,ED - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,500)}Fusion chikara no hitotsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:25.86,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Strachem jsem ochromen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:29.57,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ale nikdy zcela nevyhraje
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:32.99,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Kvůli tomu jsem rozhodnut se smát
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:36.37,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Přinést světlo do temnoty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:40.04,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Mé rozhodnutí mě vede
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:43.63,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I když je to cesta osamělá
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:47.34,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I když jsem na pochybách
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:51.35,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Stále jdu směrem kupředu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.06,0:22:55.85,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Beru sebou touhu nikdy nikoho neztratit
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:59.60,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ať už minulou, současnou nebo budoucí
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:03.15,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Překonám tuto nekonečnou cestu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:07.78,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}A přeměním zoufalství v naději
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:11.82,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Možné je, že hrdina povstane
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:15.12,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Je to on, kdo vás bude chránit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:19.17,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}A proti soupeřům, kterým se postaví
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:23.80,ED - CZ,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,500)}Použije sílu přátelství
